content:
Add the Wrap Up Component to the Messaging Session Record Page

To let agents generate and view the messaging session summaries, add the Wrap-Up component to the Messaging Session record page in the console.

To customize action layouts and page layouts:	Customize Application

Open the Lightning App Builder. Next to the messaging session record page, click Edit. Drag Einstein Field Recommendations component on to the record page. In the Recommendation Type field, select Wrap-Up. In the Update Action field, select the update action that you created to store the summaries. Click Save | Activation, and close the Org Defaults pop-up window.
